data.description: One of the most affordably priced 3 bedroom homes with a pool in the area. Now's your chance! On nearly 1/5 acre, this home with a SPARKLING POOL and a Florida room is perfect for those who love barbeques and pool parties! EXPLORE THE HOME WITH THE VIDEO TOUR LINK. Through the front door, beautiful TILE FLOORING runs throughout the living space. A large family room leads not only to your dining space, but in to your kitchen, where the family cook will have plenty of counter space for meal prep, and gorgeous NEW STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES! A second family room leads out to the FLORIDA ROOM, enclosed with windows for great year-round living. Use it as your home gym, or create a sitting area to enjoy your morning coffee.  Your screened pool deck has plenty of room for outdoor furniture and is a great place to fire up the grill, as well as cool off with friends and family in your refreshing pool. The house features a SPLIT FLOORPLAN with the primary suite spanning the length of the house on one side, and the 2 secondary bedrooms and secondary bath on the other. The A/C is approximately 5 years old and the pool pump was recently replaced. Poinciana is a great community and you are just a few minutes from a Walmart Supercenter, Publix, banks, and restaurants. The neighborhood has an amazing Amenities Center just around the corner from the house, where residents can pay a reduced rate to use a top rate gym, aquatic center, and more. Come experience the life you’ve always wanted to live!
